2006;;Danny Roane: First Time Director;;American;;Andy Dick;;Andy Dick, Frankie Muniz, Jack Black;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Danny_Roane:_First_Time_Director;;After being blackballed from Hollywood because of his drunken antics, Danny Roane, a washed up TV actor, sobers up to direct his first feature film. As the pressure builds, Roane turns to the bottle again and attempts to finish his movie about drug and alcohol abuse. But in his drunken madness, he decides to make the film a musical.